{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/chaining-if-else-statements","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Povezivanje If Else Iskaza","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p><code>if/else</code> iskazi se mogu povezati za slozeniju logiku. Evo <dfn>pseudokoda</dfn> za vise povezanih <code>if</code> / <code>else if</code> iskaza:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">if (condition1) {\n  statement1\n} else if (condition2) {\n  statement2\n} else if (condition3) {\n  statement3\n. . .\n} else {\n  statementN\n}\n</code></pre>\n</section>","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244dc","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Napisi povezane <code>if</code>/<code>else if</code> iskaze koji ispunjavaju sledece uslove:</p>\n<p><code>num &#x3C; 5</code> - vrati <code>Tiny</code>\n<code>num &#x3C; 10</code> - vrati <code>Small</code>\n<code>num &#x3C; 15</code> - vrati <code>Medium</code>\n<code>num &#x3C; 20</code> - vrati <code>Large</code>\n<code>num >= 20</code> - vrati <code>Huge</code></p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":16772,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/chaining-if-else-statements"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function testSize(num) {\n  // Only change code below this line\n\n\n  return \"Change Me\";\n  // Only change code above this line\n}\n\ntestSize(7);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Treba da imate najmanje cetiri <code>else</code> iskaza</p>","testStr